Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十九话\N史上最强的宿敌\N袭击而来的无情之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧好像退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再拿水来换
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.01,0:02:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦  左之助现在怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经退烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.85,0:02:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要静养就应该没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  这样我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.12,0:02:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么人对左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.69,0:02:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下这么狠毒的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.14,0:02:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤究竟为何不直接找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而要如此对待左之助呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.28,0:02:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道他有什么目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了  请慢用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.66,0:03:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中午只吃一碗面太少了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢中午吃面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.74,0:03:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你以后叫我藤田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是赤末先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找我有何贵干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.71,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涉海老板要我来看看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.09,0:03:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件工作是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.46,0:03:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是一听到你的名气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.06,0:03:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果就变成让你来干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.23,0:03:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我看你不怎么顺眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好  你行的话就快点解决掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.97,0:03:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么要吩咐的话\N就尽快说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.60,0:03:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,免得到时候我被人放冷剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于你的不满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到失敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么就让我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起联手来打击敌人吧\N怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.85,0:04:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你要我怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.83,0:04:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次我去神谷道场时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故意的留下了一些线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在他应该发现我的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.21,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但还不知道我的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.74,0:04:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我把这封信带去给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他引出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我去引他出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能把他杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.19,0:04:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就和你平分酬劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.76,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心 向来是你的头号大敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此轻易的让我来解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我曾对涉海说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心是我的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事实上他在我眼中已微不足道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我最大的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.05,0:05:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是好好的过完我的下半辈子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.82,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与其冒险换取高额赏金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如可以确确实实的领到花用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我并不想帮你做这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲你这句话我就帮你一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.87,0:05:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但仅此一次  下不为例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这只井底之蛙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不把你放在眼中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.77,0:06:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰要你去买豆腐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点事要出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能会晚点回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.35,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上记得把门窗关好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那我不是要去买豆腐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我又不是没事做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.77,0:06:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤  你终于要出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.94,0:06:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要看你究竟在玩什么把戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.94,0:07:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是绯村剑心  好快的身手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.68,0:07:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤末有人  来取你的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心有事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.55,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说要晚点回来\N喏豆腐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.69,0:07:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还有没有说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  他还看了一封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.20,0:07:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  是情书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是女孩子写给他的情书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.07,0:07:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪剑心什么也不说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好真的会很晚才回来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  人家好不容易买来的豆腐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差点被你摔坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助现在受伤躺在床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心哪有心情去约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗？丑女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.92,0:08:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我怎么都没想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真笨  真笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.14,0:08:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有位叫绯村拔刀斋的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么会知道剑心的绰号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.11,0:08:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是这里的巡佐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫藤田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是从署长那儿听到\N有关绯村的事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.99,0:08:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是署长的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我们接到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.77,0:08:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人要暗杀他的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我可以在这等一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心可能晚点回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有人要你来杀我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.00,0:09:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人是没有缘由就杀人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先请你说个清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缘由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.87,0:09:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你死后自然会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样我就抓不到你\N在左边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得见我就快来抓我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.05,0:09:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不信你的速度会比我快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.99,0:09:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想动得那么快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.66,0:10:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快说  是谁让你来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回答  你到底想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟斋藤又是什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.95,0:10:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是受人指使的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是斋藤那家伙威协我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤那家伙到底想做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的话我全相信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后就快改过自新吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你这么好骗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中计了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.18,0:10:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子看你怎么跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.88,0:10:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.95,0:10:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双手被反绑的滋味如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.95,0:10:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且完全动弹不得了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比速度 你比我快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比力气 你就比不过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人想暗杀剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.31,0:11:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 也是那个人 把左之助打成重伤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.65,0:11:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果真如此的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.65,0:11:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他们一定非常强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.35,0:11:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要特别小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.56,0:11:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道剑心现在怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心是个机灵的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.56,0:11:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必替他担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万不可随便出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有巡佐在此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在屋内比出去安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为警官只带西洋剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还会带武士刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.29,0:12:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西洋剑哪有武士刀好用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是经过特别允许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.93,0:12:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以佩带日本刀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也算是厉害的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死的有点可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就照约定\N告诉你杀你的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和斋藤他们一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是被政客派来杀你的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.07,0:12:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我不该让你知道原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.84,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在黑笠事件之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让政客他们知道了你的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是他们害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.91,0:13:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幕府时代干过的坏事 被你揭穿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.48,0:13:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些政客们全都是一些\N做过见不得人的事的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.92,0:13:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪有人说斋藤是新撰组内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀手的不二人选
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.90,0:13:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是装死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这个时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有像你这样的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.97,0:13:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.01,0:13:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我摔死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.91,0:14:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好担心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.85,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后尽量少出门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.72,0:14:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外头有人想暗杀你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪听来的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.36,0:14:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察署长派人来通知我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.96,0:14:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一个叫藤田五郎的巡佐\N告诉我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.31,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对付赤末那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花了你不少的力气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.35,0:14:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离最后一次对决\N应该也有十年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 你认识藤田巡佐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.42,0:14:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你现在叫藤田五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用说的好短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用活的倒是好长的时间啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩 要腐化一个人也相当够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.87,0:15:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇藤阵也\N是你第一个杀掉的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你以前不是这种作风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.41,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去的你是个毫无缺点\N作风坚强的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要在决斗时\N总是正大光明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正面迎敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会使用伤害敌手之亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让其动摇心志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄小把戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还打算以之为人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.46,0:15:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等的卑劣手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已算不上是真正的武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.21,0:15:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只不过是新撰组\N第三队队长斋藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.01,0:15:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新撰组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来他就是.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要暗杀剑心的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你不只武功退步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连头脑都退化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我跟赤末那种人相提并论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们够格吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.55,0:16:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道他们是什么东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.15,0:16:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们新撰组比谁都清楚\N你绯村拔刀斋的功力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.32,0:16:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的你\N比赤末好得了多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.96,0:16:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为浪客让你变得脆弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.04,0:16:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只想保护好我身边的人就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已决定洗手不干剑客了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.85,0:16:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么多强都没有必要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.62,0:17:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你没有资格成为浪客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和赤末苦战时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已来这很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自称为警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.97,0:17:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友们也都深信不疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.24,0:17:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果要杀他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只这次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫时也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,观柳时也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.25,0:17:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你眼前的一切\N随时都会被夺走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.13,0:17:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电十太的一太刃的时候也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拱手让人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.04,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人怎么这么清楚\N剑心过去的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个\N满嘴仁义道德的伪君子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.48,0:18:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说些虚伪的谎话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说  只要剑心在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会保护我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.95,0:18:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是有剑心在的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把他解决掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好大惊小怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.78,0:18:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年对我来说是很漫长的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.25,0:18:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但总比你沉沦于\N自以为是的正义中要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武士如果不杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何能守护正义呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.76,0:18:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道忘了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们联手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.77,0:19:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人世间才有真正的正义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于目前的乱象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.81,0:19:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道还能视若无睹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.45,0:19:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.05,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不会再杀人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.89,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.96,0:19:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才说的都是白说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想让这姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.74,0:19:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死在我的牙突剑下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.43,0:19:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要的只是我的命而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是无法避免的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.94,0:20:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.97,0:21:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流 龙槌闪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心还是很厉害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.21,0:21:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你往哪逃 拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牙突剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
